    "central_idea": "The quiet key 1.Rcc3! preserves two distinct forced selfmating mechanisms. Queen continuations on h5/g4 compel the battery-opening ...Nf3#, while rook switchbacks off d3 compel ...Nd3#, opening the same black rook line toward the white king. Black queen and h-pawn defences select the required white continuation and mating square.",
